C. Future Work (Saran / Penelitian Selanjutnya)
The oracle analysis indicates that the principal path to improvement is richer, live features that are causally linked to per-query performance — for example, an exponentially-weighted moving average of each resolver's recent latency and a recent-failure indicator — rather than additional static hostname attributes. Further directions include collection from multiple vantage points and ISPs across Indonesia, extension to encrypted transports (DoH/DoT), and online adaptation of the model as network conditions drift.


